title: When God Blinks
itunes:title: When God Blinks
itunes:subtitle: The Creepypasta Anthology
description:
For centuries, humanity has looked to the sky and wondered, wondered what is out there. What happens when whatever is out there, sends us a message? Who will hear it?

***

Credited to CharminglyShallow and guest narrated by Owen McCuen

***

Subscribe to the show on YouTube at: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCQ3SrH_3fsROXFAjomKcUtw
